channel.title: Comments on: Webinars about the NLM Administrative Supplement for Informationists grants

item.title: By: Julia Kochi

item.description: A third webinar has been added to the series. It will take place on Friday, Oct. 25 at 11am in rm. 201. It will feature updates from 3 of the remaining informationists.
